chemo_detail:
2010 For Left Breast: Received 6 cycles of ADCT with Docetaxel + Doxorubicin from
24.11.2010 up to 10.03.2011 at Apollo. 2019 for Right Breast: Started Weekly Paclitaxel from 23.03.2019,
Week 12 till 10/06/19. Started Single Gemcitabine (D1 & D8) C1 from 01.07.2019. Cycle 6 Day 8 due on
06/11/19. Cycle 12 Inj. Zoledronic acid 23/02/20. On Tab Tamona.
